00:27:16,839 --> 00:27:19,079
Actions speak louder than words.

578
00:27:20,240 --> 00:27:21,319
The case is over,

579
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:21,960
and I won't
bother you anymore.

580
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:25,000
Goodbye, Lawyer Xu.

581
00:27:35,039 --> 00:27:35,720
Pipi,

582
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:38,359
What should we do now?

583
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:04,440
Ruan Yu,

584
00:28:26,799 --> 00:28:27,559
are you okay?

585
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,119
Mingying,

586
00:28:36,799 --> 00:28:37,519
what's wrong?

587
00:28:38,759 --> 00:28:40,039
I can delete the friend,

588
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,640
but what about my novel?

589
00:28:44,720 --> 00:28:46,200
My inspiration is gone.

590
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:48,240
I can't

591
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:49,640
write anymore.

592
00:28:50,559 --> 00:28:51,480
I understand.

593
00:28:52,079 --> 00:28:53,440
The male lead has fallen,

594
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,599
how can you continue writing?

595
00:28:59,519 --> 00:29:00,440
Maybe

596
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,640
just keep delaying the update.

597
00:29:06,559 --> 00:29:08,279
But the readers are all waiting.

598
00:29:11,599 --> 00:29:14,119
And the deadline in the contract

599
00:29:14,119 --> 00:29:15,039
with your publisher

600
00:29:15,319 --> 00:29:16,480
is

601
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,279
getting closer and closer.

602
00:29:19,720 --> 00:29:21,039
Don't worry about me.

603
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:22,279
I can handle the chief editor.

604
00:29:23,759 --> 00:29:25,440
As for the readers,

605
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:28,680
if you force yourself to write now,

606
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:30,319
but it'll be a mess.

607
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,480
Isn't that
even more irresponsible?

608
00:29:36,279 --> 00:29:36,839
Just

609
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,720
explain it well,

610
00:29:40,079 --> 00:29:40,960
apologize to everyone,

611
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:43,359
and they'll understand.

612
00:30:09,519 --> 00:30:10,880
[I've made an appointment with Mr. Zhang]

613
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:13,119
[for 10 AM on Monday,]

614
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,440
[at this café.]

615
00:30:14,559 --> 00:30:16,200
[I'll update you on your ex's progress]

616
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:17,240
[after the meeting.]

617
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:20,240
Your friend's ex-boyfriend's progress.

618
00:30:31,440 --> 00:30:32,039
Alright.

619
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:34,960
Look.

620
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:39,279
I'd like to apologize to everyone.

621
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:41,200
I Really Want to Whisper in Your Ear

622
00:30:41,599 --> 00:30:43,480
may have to be suspended.

623
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,839
I may need some time

624
00:30:45,839 --> 00:30:46,640
to get back into the groove.

625
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,279
If I can't

626
00:30:48,359 --> 00:30:49,640
continue this story,

627
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,440
I will refund the subscription coins

628
00:30:51,759 --> 00:30:53,160
to everyone's account.

629
00:30:54,279 --> 00:30:55,960
Thank you for your

630
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:56,640
support.

631
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,440
We will

632
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:00,200
meet again.

633
00:31:02,079 --> 00:31:03,240
No, Da.

634
00:31:03,599 --> 00:31:04,440
Our hero

635
00:31:04,440 --> 00:31:05,880
hasn't found his love.

636
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,759
How can you just give up on him?

637
00:31:08,279 --> 00:31:09,279
It's okay, Da.

638
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,160
Too much

639
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,519
has happened recently.

640
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:12,640
If this story
made you sad,

641
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,960
let's start a new one.

642
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:42,279
Why are you sitting there
in the middle of the night?

643
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:44,400
Mingying

644
00:31:45,799 --> 00:31:47,240
Every time I close my eyes,

645
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:49,559
I see Xu Huaisong.

646
00:31:50,599 --> 00:31:51,279
One of them

647
00:31:51,759 --> 00:31:53,920
is like Hanazawa Rui.

648
00:31:55,039 --> 00:31:55,839
The other one

649
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:58,680
is like Daoming Si.

650
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:00,839
You can't sleep

651
00:32:00,839 --> 00:32:01,880
you are losing sleep.

652
00:32:02,279 --> 00:32:03,200
Think about him,

653
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:05,519
he might be sleeping soundly right now.

654
00:32:06,359 --> 00:32:07,160
Is it worth it?

655
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:09,680
No, it's not.

656
00:32:11,279 --> 00:32:13,200
But I can't control myself.

657
00:32:16,839 --> 00:32:18,079
You are almost

658
00:32:18,079 --> 00:32:19,319
in a state of heartbreak.

659
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:23,319
That's how it is at night.

660
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,920
But even if you can't sleep,

661
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,920
lying down is also a kind of rest.

662
00:32:31,319 --> 00:32:32,039
Come on up.

663
00:32:34,279 --> 00:32:34,960
Hurry up!

664
00:32:45,279 --> 00:32:46,079
Stop thinking.

665
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:48,440
He should be the one worrying.

666
00:33:31,119 --> 00:33:31,759
Ruan Yu.

667
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:33,400
I'm here to apologize.

668
00:33:44,599 --> 00:33:45,359
I'm sorry.

669
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:47,079
I should've told you earlier.

670
00:33:47,079 --> 00:33:48,160
I shouldn't have kept it from you.

671
00:33:49,119 --> 00:33:50,880
Leave now, or I'll call the police.

672
00:33:52,720 --> 00:33:53,160
It's him!
-Forgive me. -Hurry up!

673
00:33:54,759 --> 00:33:55,599
Stop asking!

674
00:33:55,599 --> 00:33:56,720
Hurry up, drag him away!

675
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:57,559
Let me finish!

676
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:02,839
Ms. Ruan, I'm sorry.

677
00:34:03,799 --> 00:34:05,920
I just want you to help me with...

678
00:34:06,359 --> 00:34:07,359
Bullying my daughter,

679
00:34:07,359 --> 00:34:08,599
and now you want me to help you?

680
00:34:09,519 --> 00:34:10,440
No way!

681
00:34:10,639 --> 00:34:11,119
Not even

682
00:34:13,039 --> 00:34:13,920
a window!

683
00:34:29,199 --> 00:34:29,840
[I'm sorry.]

684
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:32,039
[I should've told you sooner.]

685
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:34,519
[I want to explain to you in person.]

686
00:34:35,639 --> 00:34:38,199
[Do you have time these days?]

687
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:10,159
[Ruan Yu, I saw your Weibo post.]

688
00:35:10,639 --> 00:35:12,239
[You haven't updated your novel.]

689
00:35:12,559 --> 00:35:13,519
[Is there a reason?]

690
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:14,840
[I mean,]

691
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:15,480
[if it's]

692
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,599
[a legal issue,]

693
00:35:16,760 --> 00:35:18,159
[we can provide after-sales service.]

694
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,599
[Or]

695
00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:21,679
[is there another reason?]

696
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,000
It seems that Ruan Yu

697
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,320
isn't planning to respond to me either.

698
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:27,199
I can see it.

699
00:35:33,199 --> 00:35:34,440
Send another one.

700
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:37,960
If you consider me as your friend...

701
00:35:43,199 --> 00:35:44,599
What do you mean by "if"?

702
00:35:44,840 --> 00:35:46,280
I am his friend.

703
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:47,320
There's no "if" about it.

704
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:48,519
Just do it.

705
00:35:57,199 --> 00:35:57,800
Wait.

706
00:36:00,119 --> 00:36:00,800
Are you done?
Our schedule

707
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:02,800
is packed for today.

708
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,119
We can't afford any delays.

709
00:36:04,639 --> 00:36:05,199
Finally.

710
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:06,880
Who's been

711
00:36:07,119 --> 00:36:08,320
texting me nonstop?

712
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:18,079
Ruan Yu's reply.

713
00:36:20,559 --> 00:36:21,679
Thanks for asking, Mr. Liu.

714
00:36:22,519 --> 00:36:23,639
The hiatus is because the male lead

715
00:36:23,639 --> 00:36:24,760
has broken character for me.

716
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:27,199
I'm no longer invested in this story.

717
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,480
What does "breaking character" mean?

718
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:32,000
In this context,
it means

719
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:35,000
the character's persona

720
00:36:35,679 --> 00:36:36,480
The character collapses.

721
00:36:36,679 --> 00:36:38,320
I'm not interested in

722
00:36:39,199 --> 00:36:40,119
the male protagonist in the story.

723
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:47,159
Bro,

724
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:48,440
I can only help you up to here.

725
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:50,800
You go the rest of the way yourself.

726
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,360
By the way, this afternoon,

727
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,599
people from SG

728
00:36:57,599 --> 00:36:58,960
will come to discuss the new annual cooperation.

729
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:00,039
Don't forget.

730
00:37:06,519 --> 00:37:08,639
Jackson, welcome to Zhikun.

731
00:37:08,719 --> 00:37:09,719
Nice to meet you.

732
00:37:10,239 --> 00:37:11,000
Nice to meet you.

733
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:01,079
Don't worry.

734
00:38:01,639 --> 00:38:02,679
I'm almost home.

735
00:38:05,119 --> 00:38:05,719
How was it?
After a day of fun,

736
00:38:06,719 --> 00:38:08,119
do you feel completely relaxed

737
00:38:08,119 --> 00:38:09,239
and all your worries are gone?

738
00:38:10,679 --> 00:38:11,519
The flashy world

739
00:38:11,519 --> 00:38:13,000
is indeed the best elixir.

740
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:14,760
Tonight,

741
00:38:15,199 --> 00:38:16,280
I'm sure I'll have a good sleep.

742
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:17,599
Of course.

743
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,320
I can sleep well too.

744
00:38:20,039 --> 00:38:21,119
I'm going to take a shower.

745
00:38:21,960 --> 00:38:22,639
You should rest early.
We have work tomorrow.

746
00:38:24,039 --> 00:38:24,800
I'm home.

747
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:26,199
Love you. Bye.

748
00:38:48,519 --> 00:38:50,320
Lawyer Xu, wear this.

749
00:38:51,519 --> 00:38:52,280
It's new.

750
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:53,920
I bought it at the supermarket

751
00:38:54,119 --> 00:38:55,679
after you visited my house last time.

752
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:57,000
Thank you.

753
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:04,800
How do you know

754
00:40:05,199 --> 00:40:06,320
I'm from Suzhou?

755
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:14,039
[Ruan Yu, you're done.]

756
00:40:29,199 --> 00:40:30,480
[The effects of the pills]

757
00:40:31,159 --> 00:40:32,760
[seem to be wearing off too quickly.]

758
00:40:38,159 --> 00:40:40,760
[I think just him disappearing isn't enough.]

759
00:40:42,159 --> 00:40:45,360
[I might need to disappear as well.]

760
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:05,159
Ruan Yu.

761
00:41:08,639 --> 00:41:09,320
Ruan Yu.

762
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,320
Young man,
stop knocking.

763
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:15,159
There's no one home.

764
00:41:16,119 --> 00:41:17,440
Do you know where she went?

765
00:41:18,239 --> 00:41:19,320
How would I know?

766
00:41:19,599 --> 00:41:20,039
But this morning,
I saw her

767
00:41:20,960 --> 00:41:21,920
leaving with

768
00:41:22,079 --> 00:41:23,400
a big suitcase

769
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,119
during my workout.

770
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:25,800
She must be going on a long trip.

771
00:41:52,639 --> 00:41:53,360
Why are you here?

772
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:55,119
Why can't I come?

773
00:41:57,400 --> 00:41:59,400
What's up? You look down.

774
00:42:06,159 --> 00:42:07,840
The rumors have died down,

775
00:42:08,760 --> 00:42:10,679
and it's time to resume the novel updates.

776
00:42:11,559 --> 00:42:13,840
But I just can't write anymore.

777
00:42:14,199 --> 00:42:15,920
It's normal to get stuck when writing a novel.

778
00:42:16,119 --> 00:42:17,199
You used to get stuck too.

779
00:42:17,679 --> 00:42:18,519
Just relax.

780
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:22,199
This time is different.

781
00:42:23,199 --> 00:42:25,079
The prototype of the male lead is right beside me.

782
00:42:25,639 --> 00:42:26,280
How can I possibly

783
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,920
continue writing as if nothing happened?

784
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:30,199
Aren't you two just talking about work

785
00:42:30,199 --> 00:42:31,039
and having a video call?

786
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:31,840
What's going on?

787
00:42:33,679 --> 00:42:34,559
Did you turn Chapter 23

788
00:42:34,559 --> 00:42:35,639
into reality?

789
00:42:36,840 --> 00:42:37,800
How's that possible?

790
00:42:39,079 --> 00:42:40,159
What can't be written?

791
00:42:40,159 --> 00:42:41,119
Come on, let me see.

792
00:42:42,320 --> 00:42:43,119
I'll find it for you.
I'll find it.

793
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,119
You, just sit.

794
00:42:47,679 --> 00:42:49,280
Let me check the draft.

795
00:42:50,679 --> 00:42:51,199
Here.

796
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:53,559
Here it is.

797
00:43:01,960 --> 00:43:03,119
Ms. Ruan,

798
00:43:04,159 --> 00:43:05,840
if I'm not mistaken,

799
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:06,920
you've only updated

800
00:43:06,920 --> 00:43:08,119
like

801
00:43:08,119 --> 00:43:09,119
five

802
00:43:09,599 --> 00:43:10,559
words.

803
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:12,119
Do you even need to look for it?

804
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:16,239
The moment I open the document,

805
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:17,400
I don't think of Xu Huaisong

806
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:19,159
from high school,

807
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:21,400
but Lawyer Xu's face.

808
00:43:22,880 --> 00:43:24,000
I can even hear

809
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:25,599
his sharp comments.

810
00:43:27,320 --> 00:43:30,159
[On the day He Shiqian was on duty,]

811
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:32,719
[he deliberately sweeps slowly,]

812
00:43:33,320 --> 00:43:36,559
[because Lin Xisheng is nearby.]

813
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:39,199
[Lawyers' time is very precious.]

814
00:43:41,719 --> 00:43:43,320
[Lin Xisheng]

815
00:43:43,760 --> 00:43:47,039
[also has photos of He Shiqian]

816
00:43:47,639 --> 00:43:49,159
[taken at the sports meet]

817
00:43:49,599 --> 00:43:53,559
[in the class teacher's camera.]

818
00:43:58,760 --> 00:43:59,280
[Miss Ruan,]

819
00:43:59,280 --> 00:44:00,400
[I need to remind you that]

820
00:44:00,719 --> 00:44:01,960
[taking photos of others]

821
00:44:02,119 --> 00:44:03,920
[without their permission]

822
00:44:04,519 --> 00:44:06,079
[carries certain legal risks.]

823
00:44:11,679 --> 00:44:12,960
It's not that I don't want to write.

824
00:44:13,800 --> 00:44:15,280
I just can't

825
00:44:15,280 --> 00:44:16,599
put a word on it.

826
00:44:19,159 --> 00:44:20,360
Based on my experience,

827
00:44:21,199 --> 00:44:22,199
there are two solutions

828
00:44:22,800 --> 00:44:24,679
to this problem.

829
00:44:25,239 --> 00:44:27,079
Either stay away from him,

830
00:44:27,599 --> 00:44:28,239
or get close to him.

831
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:30,519
You can try to get close to him.

832
00:44:30,760 --> 00:44:31,800
Maybe you'll get new inspirations.

833
00:44:32,079 --> 00:44:33,360
Get close to him?

834
00:44:34,199 --> 00:44:34,639
But...
what if

835
00:44:35,400 --> 00:44:36,559
I lose interest in him?

836
00:44:37,320 --> 00:44:38,719
That's less likely

837
00:44:38,719 --> 00:44:39,559
than you
getting back together.

838
00:44:42,119 --> 00:44:43,119
I'm tired.

839
00:44:44,039 --> 00:44:45,159
I'm gonna take a nap.

840
00:44:45,800 --> 00:44:46,519
You're good.
